<dl id="n06025i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06025i">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06025i"> 25(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> priest robe &amp; bells</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">And when they all bowed themselves in prayer, the high priest went in to consult God in the usual way, <mark>taking the robe with the twelve bells</mark> into the holy of holies; and he prayed concerning her <font color="green">[B.V.M]</font>. <small> James DeQincy Donehoo, <a name="APOCD" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#APOCD"><cite title="source">Les The Apocryphal Life of Christ</cite></a> (1903) 28</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
